<tw-storydata name="Design-Story" startnode="1" creator="Twine" creator-version="2.5.1" format="Chapbook" format-version="1.2.2" ifid="1D95A5EA-2473-4F44-AB7D-55F733A20291" options="" tags="" zoom="0.6" hidden><style role="stylesheet" id="twine-user-stylesheet" type="text/twine-css"></style><script role="script" id="twine-user-script" type="text/twine-javascript"></script><tw-tag name="Expostion" color="blue"></tw-tag><tw-tag name="Introduction" color="blue"></tw-tag><tw-tag name="Plot" color="red"></tw-tag><tw-tag name="End" color="green"></tw-tag><tw-tag name="Characters" color="orange"></tw-tag><tw-tag name="Places" color="purple"></tw-tag><tw-tag name="Character-sheet" color="orange"></tw-tag><tw-tag name="Place-sheet" color="purple"></tw-tag><tw-passagedata pid="1" name="Adventure start point (Introduction)" tags="Introduction" position="600,600" size="100,100">Our story begins like any other, with a protagonist meant to have an amazing, dangerous and frenetic adventure.

~~[[Jack Olvan]]~~, our hero, is a twenty year old boy resident of ~~[[Magninsule]]~~, the biggest island of the ~~[[Stagnant Waters]]~~ archipelago. He belongs to a good standing family composed by his father, his brother and him. That&#39;s because his mother died when Jack was barely five years old, but has never been a reason for him to be weak.

Generally, his life is rather monotonous, as he is finishing his Naval Engineering studies and has not much time for anything else. However, sometimes it&#39;s not as easy as it seems, given that his group of friends is constantly getting in trouble or seeking for an adventure.

~~[[Century dilema]]~~</tw-passagedata><tw-passagedata pid="2" name="Matters of interest" tags="Introduction" position="1200,300" size="100,100">Inside his head, Jack can&#39;t stop thinking if he has taken the right choice, in thoughts of curiosity and envy asks himself where they might be his friends. What he doesn&#39;t know is that will be reunited with them shortly.

