~~[[A bumpy start]]~~</tw-passagedata><tw-passagedata pid="4" name="Century dilema" tags="Introduction" position="900,600" size="100,100">The summer break is just starting, when suddenly his calmed pace of life gets interrupted by the leader of his friends group, who comes with a brave but foolish preposition for the team.
He ensures that some brave man are being recruited around the island to fight against a dangerous group of criminals coming from Tenebris sea. The reports say that since last week they have been attacking the ports of Liberportus.

The rest of the Squad immediately understands why they are talking about such dangerous events, they are sailing into the unknown once more!
