</tw-passagedata><tw-passagedata pid="7" name="Jack Olvan" tags="Character-sheet" position="700,300" size="100,100">Jack is a boy in his twenties finishing his studies in naval engineering. Living in Magnisule has not much to worry about, his family has status, money. Even though his family is not conventional, they live happily. His mother died when Jack was very young and does not really remember much, and his little brother, Max, lately has been arguing a lot more with father about politics. Every family has its problems, but they are good with each other.

**Motivations:**
He&#39;s got enough money from his parents to not need to worry, so he&#39;s never got any motivation from work  or money wise. He still works in commerce of goods by boat,  sometimes working in contraband too. He and his friends work together and that keeps it as motivation to keep working. You could say relationships are his real motivation. Started a career with some of them. Working, hobbies, partying... He does nearly everything with them. Recently is taking a liking to his studies and is taking extra hours to do some research outside studies.

**Goals:**
Finishing the last year of studies, getting this important gig (valuable materials as presents to his friends arriving in 2 months), getting a deeper understanding of engineering and start designing a float. As you can see, Jack does not look far away in the future. He is satisfied with how things are and wants to keep it that way.

**Fears:**
The imminent break of his group of friends (marriage of 2 of them, all finishing studies, some plans to travel). Not being smart enough to design and work in naval engineering. His father cutting ties with his brother who is more rebel day by day.

**Phobias:**
Change, long goodbyes, rings and jewelry.

**Remarkable traits:**
Working and trading, negotiating, Jack developed better social abilities by force. 
Knowledge in physics and naval engineer.

**Stats:**
Jack never fought, and never even though we would have to, so it isn’t prepared at all. He is weak and does not have the stamina. But even all of this, he makes up with good weaponry and his quick mind.


